==成员国资格申请==
* {{flag|Belarus}} -2010年申请观察员地位。<ref name="OICobserversfr">{{cite web|url=http://www.oic-oci.org/oicv2/topic/?t_id=4856&t_ref=2046&lan=fr|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130802211548/http://www.oic-oci.org/oicv2/topic/?t_id=4856&t_ref=2046&lan=fr|archive-date=2013-08-02|title=Le Secrétariat général demande d'accélérer l'adoption du Règlement portant conditions d'obtention du statut d'observateur auprès de l'OCI|date=2011-01-17|accessdate=2013-08-02|publisher=[[Organisation_of_Islamic_Cooperation|Organisation of Islamic Cooperation]]|language=fr|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="B92">{{cite web|url=http://www.b92.net/eng/news/politics-article.php?yyyy=2011&mm=07&dd=01&nav_id=75211|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130221091437/http://www.b92.net/eng/news/politics-article.php?yyyy=2011&mm=07&dd=01&nav_id=75211|url-status=dead|archive-date=2013-02-21|title=Serbia requests OIC observer status|publisher=[[B92|B92]]|date=2011-07-01|accessdate=2012-11-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* {{flag|Brazil}} - 2011年申请观察员地位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ipotnews.com/index.php?jdl=Brazil_requests_to_join_OIC_as_observer_state&news_id=464169&group_news=ALLNEWS&taging_subtype=BRAZIL|title=Brazil Requests To Join OIC As Observer State|date=2011-05-16|accessdate=2013-08-02|publisher=IPOTNEWS}}</ref>
* {{flag|Central African Republic}} -  2002年申请正式成员资格。<ref name="OICobserversfr"/><ref name="CNN">{{cite web|url=http://www.caribbeannewsnow.com/topstory-Brazil-to-join-Guyana-and-Suriname-in-Islamic-bloc-6609.html|title=Brazil to join Guyana and Suriname in Islamic bloc|last=Chickrie|first=Ray|date=2011-06-13|accessdate=2012-11-28|publisher=Caribbean News Now!|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305043026/http://www.caribbeannewsnow.com/topstory-Brazil-to-join-Guyana-and-Suriname-in-Islamic-bloc-6609.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* {{flag|China}} - 2012年申请观察员地位。<ref name="New Straits Times">{{cite news|url=http://www.nst.com.my/latest/china-seeks-to-be-oic-observer-member-1.99370|title=China seeks to be OIC observer member|date=2012-06-28|accessdate=2013-08-03|newspaper=New Straits Times|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106073115/http://www.nst.com.my/latest/china-seeks-to-be-oic-observer-member-1.99370|archivedate=2012-11-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* {{flag|Democratic Republic of Congo}} - 2008年申请观察员地位，<ref name="OICobservers"/> 2011年正式成为正式成员。<ref name="B92"/>
* {{flag|India}} - 印度是穆斯林的占少数的国家，印度在伊斯兰会议组织成立时曾表现出加入伊斯兰会议组织的成员国兴趣。<ref name=alaram>Mustafa El-Feki: [http://weekly.ahram.org.eg/2005/730/ http://weekly.ahram.org.eg/2005/730/in1.htm An Indo-Arab blunder?] {{Wayback|url=http://weekly.ahram.org.eg/2005/730/ |date=20110727022735 }}[http://www.hindunet.org/hvk/articles/0207/34.html] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hindunet.org/hvk/articles/0207/34.html |date=20160306080337 }} ''Al-Ahram,'' February 17–23, 2005.</ref> 然而，它遭到巴基斯坦的反对。此后，印度从未正式申请以观察员身份或成员国身份加入伊斯兰会议组织。 <ref name=thehindu>Iran to view favourably India's entry into OIC : [http://www.thehindu.com/thehindu/2000/07/21/stories/02210008.htm] ''The Hindu''July 21, 2000.</ref> 虽然印度的潜在候选资格得到了伊斯兰会议组织一些成员的支持，<ref>[http://www.expressindia.com/news/messages.php?newsid=61844 Observer status for India at OIC: King Abdullah] {{Wayback|url=http://www.expressindia.com/news/messages.php?newsid=61844 |date=20121011122551 }} Expressindia.com, January 22, 2006.</ref> 但巴基斯坦的强烈反对和抵制伊斯兰会议组织的威胁实际上导致印度加入伊斯兰会议组织受阻。巴基斯坦外交部认为，印度加入伊斯兰会议组织将违反伊斯兰会议组织的规则，该规则要求一个有抱负的国家不应与成员国持续发生冲突。<ref>[http://www.rediff.com/news/2006/jan/23saudi1.htm Pak disapproves Saudi king's comments on India's OIC entry] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rediff.com/news/2006/jan/23saudi1.htm |date=20210108183224 }} Rediff News, January 23, 2006.</ref>
* {{flag|Kenya}} -2011年申请正式成员资格。<ref name="B92"/>
* {{flag|Liberia}} - 2016年11月申请正式成员资格。<ref name="GNNLiberia">{{cite web|url=http://gnnliberia.com/2016/11/10/liberia-seeks-membership-islamic-body/|title=Liberia Seeks Membership To Islamic Body|date=2016-11-17|accessdate=2016-11-17|publisher=[[Global_News_Network|Global News Network]]|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108183206/https://gnnliberia.com/2016/11/10/liberia-seeks-membership-islamic-body/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* {{flag|Mauritius}} - 2002年申请成为正式成员。<ref name="OICobserversfr"/><ref name="CNN"/>
* {{flag|Nepal}} - 2008年申请观察员地位。<ref name="OICobservers"/>
* {{flag|Philippines}} - 2008年申请观察员地位。<ref name="OICobservers"/> 菲律宾政府曾试图加入伊斯兰会议组织，但遭到摩洛民族解放阵线的反对。摩洛民族解放阵线是伊斯兰会议组织驻菲律宾的观察员。MNLF声称，菲律宾的成员资格是不必要的。[{{Citation needed|date=September 2010}}. 2009年，该国申办得到了印尼、伊朗、马来西亚和阿拉伯联合酋长国等机构的大力支持。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://globalnation.inquirer.net/news/news/view/20090526-207265/RP-nears-observer-status-in-OIC----DFA |title=RP nears observer status in OIC - DFA - INQUIRER.net, Philippine News for Filipinos |publisher=Globalnation.inquirer.net |date=2009-05-26 |accessdate=2011-03-25 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404022243/http://globalnation.inquirer.net/news/news/view/20090526-207265/RP-nears-observer-status-in-OIC----DFA |archivedate=2015-04-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mb.com.ph/node/202546 |title=EZ2 Lotto Luzon | Manila Bulletin |publisher=Mb.com.ph |date=2009-04-15 |accessdate=2011-03-25 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225065252/https://mb.com.ph/node/202546 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.philstar.com/Article.aspx?articleId=472375&publicationSubCategoryId=205 |title=RP closer to becoming observer-state in Organization of Islamic Conference | Home >> The Filipino Global Community >> Philippines |publisher=Philstar.com |date=2009-05-29 |accessdate=2011-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603143753/http://www.philstar.com/Article.aspx?articleId=472375&publicationSubCategoryId=205 |archive-date=2016-06-03 |url-status=dead |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gmanews.tv/story/162925/DFA-Technicalities-blocking-RP-bid-for-OIC-observer-status |title=DFA: ‘Technicalities’ blocking RP bid for OIC observer status - Nation - GMA News Online - Latest Philippine News |publisher=Gmanews.tv |date= |accessdate=2011-03-25 |archive-date=2018-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225065258/https://www.gmanetwork.com/news/news/nation/162925/dfa-technicalities-blocking-rp-bid-for-oic-observer-status/story/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2019年，MNLF领导人之一尼尔·米苏阿里被任命为该组织的特使。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.abs-cbn.com/news/12/14/19/duterte-appoints-misuari-as-special-envoy-to-international-islamic-agency|title=Duterte appoints Misuari as special envoy to international Islamic agency|last=News|first=ABS-CBN|website=ABS-CBN News|access-date=2019-12-14|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108183247/https://news.abs-cbn.com/news/12/14/19/duterte-appoints-misuari-as-special-envoy-to-international-islamic-agency|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* {{flag|Serbia}} -  2008年申请观察员地位。<ref name="OICobservers"/>
* {{flag|South Africa}} - 2002年申请观察员地位。<ref name="OICobservers">{{cite web|url=http://www.oic-oci.org/oicv2/topic/?t_id=4857|title=OIC Secretary General Calls for Early Adoption of Rules for Access to Observer Status|date=2011-01-17|accessdate=2013-08-02|publisher=[[Organisation_of_Islamic_Cooperation|Organisation of Islamic Cooperation]]}}{{dead link|date=January 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>
* {{flag|Sri Lanka}} - 2008年申请观察员地位。<ref name="OICobservers"/>

